            "detailed_description": "In Piloteer, a whimsical and serenely challenging physics-based game about learning to fly, a renowned inventor is determined to overcome the stigma associated with flying a jetpack and convince the world that jetpacks should be revered by all.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBlending elements of both physics and trick-based games, players will need to maneuver their state-of-the-art jetpack through the skies while completing a myriad of increasingly difficult missions to change public perceptions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers will find themselves immersed in a wholly integrated physics simulation, making the beautiful world around them feel dynamic, unpredictable, and alive.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRidiculous failure is imminent in Piloteer, making the accomplishments along the way feel all the more rewarding. Put on your jetpack and take to the skies!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEATURES<br />\r\n• Increasingly challenging gameplay with sixty different missions<br />\r\n• Three beautiful environments to fly around in<br />\r\n• Career and Free Fly modes<br />\r\n• Custom-composed, serene piano score<br />\r\n• Silly and ridiculous physics-based ragdoll effects",
